 MOVE 3401
 AFFECT 3401
 ECHO OTHERS %n steps onto the platform.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB EXAMINE 8
 IFITEM 8
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER On the platform you see...
  SHOWROOM 3401
 ENDIF
ENDIF
