NUMBER 3406
NAME Karthemos, Hall of Statues
DEEPCAVE
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
The once polished and sparkling marble that makes up the walls of this hall has faded with the passage of time into a crumbling mass of matte stone. Nearby an arch that is covered by sheet of shimmering silvery liquid. Light refracted through the liquid flashes throughout the hall giving the illusion of being under water. A large statue stands before the arch as if it had just stepped through. Further down the hall, you can faintly see the silhouettes of more statues.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;ITEMS
;door
ITEM 0 943 ADJ1=317 ADJ2=210 ADJ3=312 VAL1=999 VAL2=3405 VAL3=999 CLOSED LOCKED
;ARCH
ITEM 1 60 ADJ1=312 VAL2=3410
EXTEND 1 covered by a shimmering sheet of silvery liquid
;Statue
ITEM 2 346 ADJ1=312
EXTEND 2 of a gladiator holding a net and a long trident
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
The doorway, which spans only a two and a half foot width, rises thirty or forty feet in height. It is constructed of a single immense slab of cut and dressed stone, and would be considered a marvel in any age.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
This hulking figure wears a small bronze half-helm and a kilt made of strips which are currently stone. In his hand he wields a fifteen foot trident while an intricately carved entangling net hangs loosely at his side. You notice sharp horns protruding from holes in the temples of the strange half-helm.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB LOOK 1
 CLEARVERB
 IFVAR FLAG3 = 0
  ECHO PLAYER The shimmering curtain of liquid obscures any details through the archway.
 ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER You peer through the shimmering liquid...
  SHOWROOM 3410
  ECHO OTHERS %n peers through the arch.
 ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB OPEN 0
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER The door barely moves as you press against it with one hand.
 ECHO OTHERS The door barely moves as %n presses against it with one hand.
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PUSH 0
 CLEARVERB
 EQUAL ROUNDTIME 20
 POSITION LAY
 ECHO PLAYER You apply all your weight to the door as it slowly creaks open spilling you out onto the ledge.
 ECHO OTHERS %n backs up and heaves %iself against the door spilling out onto the ledge behind it.
 MOVEGROUP 3403
 AFFECT 3403
 ECHO OTHERS Someone spills out onto the ledge from behind the door!
 PLREVENT 1
 CONTPLREVENT
