   ECHO PLAYER You recall hearing an ancient myth cycle of the terrible depredations performed by the beast known only as The Gorganth.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  ECHO OTHERS %n looks pensive but seems to give up with a blank look.
  ECHO PLAYER You do not possess enough knowledge to recall anything.
 ENDIF
ENDIF

