;
;
NUMBER 3427
NAME Tiny Chamber
REGION 150
DEEPCAVE
CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This is a tiny chamber that has been carefully creafted by skilled artisans. The stone walls, floor and ceiling are carved with intricate yet inexplicable figures. A hole leads back into the maze of tunnels.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 79 VAL2=3423
EXTEND 0 in the wall of the chamber
ITEM 1 238 ADJ1=287 ADJ2=25
EXTEND 1 set into the floor of the chamber
MONSTER_GROUP 37

IFVERB SEARCH -1
 ECHO PLAYER You notice a black rune set into the floor.
ENDIF

IFVERB RECALL 1
 IFVAR SKILL32 > 0
  ECHO OTHERS %n looks pensive for a moment.
  SKILLCHECK 32 -20 TANNRECALL
  IFVAR TANNRECALL > 0
   ECHO PLAYER It appears to you that a judicious application of mental energy will unravel the rune.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  ECHO OTHERS %n looks pensive but seems to give up with a blank look.
  ECHO PLAYER You do not possess enough knowledge to recall anything.
 ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PROJECT 1
 IFVAR SKILL26 > 5
  IFVAR ITEMADJ1 ! 374
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER As you concentrate on the rune it cracks in half!
   ECHO OTHERS %n shatters the rune with %h mind!
   SETITEMADJ 1 1 374
   ADD DIGWARDS 1
   AFFECT 3409
   ECHO ALL One of the glowing runes suddenly goes dim.
   IFVAR DIGWARDS = 4
    ECHO ALL The wall of darkness shudders as The Gorganth is freed!%c>%cThe Gorganth slithers in with a hiss!
    GENMON 361
    GMMSG ** %n just released The Gorganth keptain!
    AFFECT 3427
    ECHO ALL The caves seem to grow darker.
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The rune is already broken.
 ENDIF
ENDIF

