You stand beneath a brilliant yellow sky on some sort of strange, ancient plaza. The plaza itself rests upon a plateau which rises sharply above a vast ancient civilization. In all directions the city spreads out before you yet you can see no way to descend. There is an arch set into a large marble pillar and is covered in a sheet of shimmering silvery liquid.
